    <item>
      <title>【動畫電影】以歌聲貫串青春與回憶的科幻小品─《讓我聽見愛的歌聲》觀影心得</title>
      <link>https://kalinlai-void.github.io/ACGN/posts/sing-a-bit-of-harmony-reviews/</link>
